- Her health's fragile.

172
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:35,284
lt's her cornea. She has keratitis.

173
00:16:36,912 --> 00:16:37,787
ls she blind?

174
00:16:39,123 --> 00:16:40,331
lt's an inflammation.

175
00:16:41,792 --> 00:16:44,043
