221
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:49,223
What did you bring from America?

222
00:21:49,433 --> 00:21:50,474
An American.

223
00:21:50,809 --> 00:21:51,809
What's his name?

224
00:21:52,728 --> 00:21:55,396
Edith, please!

225
00:21:56,148 --> 00:21:59,650
Like her song,
she's "carried away by the crowd"...

226
